Apa?

985
01:10:05,793 --> 01:10:08,418
Ini lagumu juga, Farleigh. Selesaikanlah.

986
01:10:10,209 --> 01:10:11,751
Jika kau bersikeras.

987
01:10:14,001 --> 01:10:18,376
<i>Kau membawaku ke restoran di luar Broadway</i>

988
01:10:18,376 --> 01:10:20,459
