- Tak masalah.
- Kami bisa tinggal.

1130
01:21:29,876 --> 01:21:31,334
Kami ingin tinggal.

1131
01:21:31,751 --> 01:21:34,543
Ollie, minum obat saja.

1132
01:21:42,668 --> 01:21:44,168
Aku suka spageti bolognese.

1133
