- Ya?

1149
01:23:26,709 --> 01:23:27,834
Anggrek.

1150
01:23:30,293 --> 01:23:31,501
Hai!

1151
01:23:39,376 --> 01:23:40,709
Itu putri George.

1152
01:23:42,334 --> 01:23:44,626
Sayang. Dia seperti ibunya.

1153
01:24:10,209 --> 01:24:11,709
Apa kau melihat Felix?

1154
01:24:12,751 --> 01:24:13,751
Tidak.

1155
